00:00:09.762 --> 00:00:11.001
with our situation, etcetera.

00:00:11.002 --> 00:00:12.081
That being said, though,

00:00:12.082 --> 00:00:13.041
yeah, it's true,

00:00:13.042 --> 00:00:15.041
not all men are gonna be able to provide.

00:00:15.042 --> 00:00:18.641
Which is why it is so important to be very choosey

00:00:18.642 --> 00:00:20.721
and picky with who you marry.

00:00:20.722 --> 00:00:22.321
Marriage is not something to take lightly.

00:00:22.322 --> 00:00:24.001
It is not just a piece of paper.

00:00:24.002 --> 00:00:26.641
